Kisii Governor James Ongwae (pictured) is in the US to meet investors. The Council of Governors organised the trip in conjunction with the East African Chamber of Commerce to woo investors. Four other governors from Kenya will join Ongwae.A sizeable number of people from the Kisii community lives in the US. Ongwae will meet the Minnesota State Fire Department as a follow-up to agreements reached last December on fire safety training and equipment.